data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Charming single level 3-bed, 2-bath home with open floor plan, 9' ceilings, covered front & back porches, low maintenance yards. Primary suite features vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet, ensuite with dual sinks & linen closet. Great room boasts gas fireplace & vaulted ceilings, arched doorways, and laminate flooring throughout. Kitchen offers craftsman cabinets & granite counters. Central AC, farmhouse doors, great schools & easy I-5 access for commuters. Ideal for comfortable, stylish living!
